class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n涼麵喺台灣算係平民小食嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n35至$50台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係香港要將個台幣轉做港幣先食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n涼麵跟返台灣都係麻醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青瓜都好爽脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得個芝麻香唔夠濃厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係比較鍾意台北嘅陳家涼麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排骨即係香港嘅豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非常之大塊應該有兩個人嘅份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且醃得入味咬落都夠多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉質都算幾嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食落個人中好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:47:07.000Z","msg":"姐姐呢屌你老無"},{"pid":"54cc960c624970704e38a7904d11d0be7a6388e1","tid":2246461,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"灑少少白芝麻咪夠香"},{"pid":"46be4185e6d4e56bed3ea120690d7e678f88f880","tid":2246461,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b161741a2b5920f5af8837ed2ccbee8a0d0ea98","tid":2246461,"uid":25614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"623<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cda1cc4a217ff064a7f5c8aedab159a0c6cea7","tid":2246461,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco